AUDIO: 'But, here\'s the thing. By default, the agent has access to an empty workspace. To give it access to your code base, you need to set up an environment. You can run the oz create environment'

[03:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'command. This accepts a list of Git repositories you want the agent to access, or you can run it inside of a repository. The agent will scan your code base and'

[03:37] [scene:talk]
